{"tid":1070524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=紅人！狂徒闖旺角茶記淋油　女收銀員變紅人","createTime":"2019-03-20T17:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T22:56:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b601a105400527210c80a59b3d2df06073ebb7ab","tid":1070524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"（20日）晚上10時許，一名30餘歲男子手持一個載有紅色漆油的紙杯，突然走入旺角西洋菜南街107號一間茶餐廳衝向收銀櫃枱，不由分說向姓簡（68歲）女職員淋潑，她猝不及防下，身體及衣服染紅，對方繼而向她襲擊，得逞後，轉身走出門口截乘的士逃走。<br />\n<br />\n警員到場調查，召救護車將簡婦送院檢驗及清理油漬，事件中收銀枱亦被紅油濺及，警方在店外行人路檢獲載紅油紙杯，正調查茶餐廳是否曾與人有糾紛，抑或涉及事主的私人恩怨，同時翻看茶餐廳的閉路電視以追緝涉案者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190321/bkn-20190321003413177-0321_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190321%2Fbkn-20190321003413177-0321_00822_001.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOVwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=fefbe522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190321/bkn-20190321003413177-0321_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"671e9cb85e1a59f6166e8cc835a4d03fe6cb8ebf","tid":1070524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190321/photo/bkn-20190321003413177-0321_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190321005228\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190321003413177-0321_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190321005228&h=fcc67ccc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6acd63d53286cfdf77aadc42c6de9ef9f2823b8","tid":1070524,"uid":103759,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">紅油紙杯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 